text: Mohammad Khan Junejo (Urdu: , Sindhi :محمد خان جوڻيجو, August 18 1932 – March 16 1993) was a Pakistani politician and statesman who served as the tenth prime minister of Pakistan from 1985 to 1988, under president Muhammad Zia-ul- Haq. == References == Category:1932 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Pakistan Category:Politicians from Karachi
title: Muhammad Khan Junejo
